      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Register/Login -> User + ClientProfile\n2. Create project -> Project model in MongoDB\n3. Project starts with kbsSync = not_synced\n4. Click Sync Project to KBS -> /api/kbs/projects/[id]/sync\n5. Python derives roles + team size from title, description, skills\n6. Neo4j gets Client, Project, Skill, Role nodes\n7. Project page asks recommended freelancers + teams\n8. RecSys returns skill match, team coverage, synergy, and explanations",
