      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Neo4j Knowledge Graph\n\n(Client)-[:POSTED_PROJECT]->(Project)\n(Project)-[:REQUIRES_SKILL]->(Skill)\n(Project)-[:REQUIRES_ROLE {count}]->(Role)\n(Freelancer)-[:HAS_SKILL]->(Skill)\n(Freelancer)-[:MATCHES_ROLE {score}]->(Role)\n(Freelancer)-[:WORKED_AT]->(Company)\n(Freelancer)-[:STUDIED_AT]->(Institution)\n(Freelancer)-[:CREATED_CV_PROJECT]->(CvProject)",
